  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Diosta yupaychana kay santo wasimpi
 Takuy sonqowan./
 /Diosninchejqa muñan tukuy kallpanchejwan
 Yupaychanata./
 
[V2]
 /Diosman chimpaykuna munayninman jiña
 Kawsananchejpaj./
 /Diosqa noqanchejwan tuta p’unchay kashan.
 Gloria Señorman./
 
</lyrics></song>